242
00:30:57,480 --> 00:30:59,511
Small tricks!

243
00:31:02,640 --> 00:31:07,359
You've been an assassin for many years, and you've only learned these skills?

244
00:31:07,359 --> 00:31:12,479
Liar. What you've learned all these years isn't much better than me.

245
00:31:12,479 --> 00:31:16,059
When did I lie? When did I become a liar?

246
00:31:16,059 --> 00:31:19,511
Observation is the basic quality of top assassins.

247
00:31:19,511 --> 00:31:24,159
If you encounter a disease that you can't cure, you will only study hard to find a solution.

248
00:31:24,159 --> 00:31:27,299
You wouldn't say no to it. Why did you lie?

249
00:31:27,299 --> 00:31:28,580
I…

250
00:31:31,440 --> 00:31:36,419
Father, you have a solution. Right? Can't you help Lu Ping?

251
00:31:37,520 --> 00:31:41,219
I can't undo it. Why do you care so much?

252
00:31:41,219 --> 00:31:43,959
Can you not undo it or are you afraid of getting into trouble with the Mountain and Sea Gang?

253
00:31:43,960 --> 00:31:45,260
You…

254
00:31:47,120 --> 00:31:51,939
Father, do you know why for so many years, I would rather be an assassin in the pugilist world

255
00:31:51,939 --> 00:31:53,880
than to stay in Carefree Valley?

256
00:31:53,880 --> 00:31:58,311
It's because I don't want to see you like this. You have had such great medical skills since I was young,

257
00:31:58,311 --> 00:32:02,559
yet you never want to go out of the valley to cure others. You'd rather stay here in this valley and make medicine.

258
00:32:02,559 --> 00:32:06,799
You're afraid of getting into trouble. Don't you want to be a hero or do something big in your lifetime?

259
00:32:06,799 --> 00:32:10,500
What do you know? I told you to leave it alone so leave it alone.

260
00:32:10,500 --> 00:32:15,139
You and Lu Ping just stay in Carefree Valley. Don't mess with that Mountain and Sea Gang.

261
00:32:15,139 --> 00:32:18,639
If anything happens to him again. I really can't save him! Understand?

262
00:32:18,639 --> 00:32:21,879
I wouldn't stay here if it wasn't for saving Lu Ping this time around.

263
00:32:21,880 --> 00:32:26,959
I am destined to be a hero unlike you, a coward.

264
00:32:36,640 --> 00:32:38,771
Yes.

265
00:32:38,771 --> 00:32:44,591
My son wants to be a hero, but I am a coward.

266
00:32:56,880 --> 00:33:01,791
The old man is feeling uneasy and won't help undo Lu Ping's lock either.

267
00:33:01,791 --> 00:33:06,671
In this case, how can I tell him that Qin Sang has been poisoned with cold toxin?

268
00:33:06,671 --> 00:33:09,860
If the boss rushes out of the valley and something happens,

269
00:33:09,860 --> 00:33:12,431
Su Tang will definitely beat me to death.

270
00:33:14,100 --> 00:33:16,071
Why would I beat you?

271
00:33:16,071 --> 00:33:20,280
Master, I am just here to entertain you.

272
00:33:20,280 --> 00:33:25,551
You can beat me whenever you want. Don't worry about me. Oh right! How is the boss doing?

273
00:33:25,551 --> 00:33:30,139
I asked him to get some rest, but he is still feeling restless.

274
00:33:30,139 --> 00:33:34,560
How about I write to Miss Qin and ask her to come here to accompany Lu Ping?

275
00:33:34,560 --> 00:33:36,100
Master, don't.

276
00:33:37,860 --> 00:33:41,560
Mo Lin, what exactly are you hiding?

277
00:33:41,560 --> 00:33:44,671
Don't think that just because this is your home I dare not beat you.

278
00:33:44,671 --> 00:33:50,060
Master, here is the thing. I have a friend who is very sick,

279
00:33:50,060 --> 00:33:54,179
but she doesn't want to be a burden to others so she asked me to hide the secret.

280
00:33:54,179 --> 00:33:57,231
If you were me, would you agree?

281
00:33:59,700 --> 00:34:03,819
Aren't your friends just us? Who is sick?

282
00:34:03,819 --> 00:34:07,811
Mo Lin, are you hiding something from me?

283
00:34:07,811 --> 00:34:12,619
By the way, Master, you haven't answered me yet. I asked before if you would be my wife.

284
00:34:12,619 --> 00:34:18,439
Didn't you say you'd answer me after we rescued the boss? Now, it's time for you to live up to your promise.

285
00:34:18,439 --> 00:34:21,760
I… Let's wait until my brother undoes the Pneuma Confinement before discussing this.

286
00:34:21,760 --> 00:34:26,609
Master, you are someone's master. You should keep your word.

287
00:34:27,770 --> 00:34:31,079
It's late. I have to go back and take care of my brother.

288
00:34:31,840 --> 00:34:35,540
Master, take care of the boss.

289
00:34:35,540 --> 00:34:37,390
I will figure out everything else.

290
00:34:37,390 --> 00:34:42,190
Don't forget. I am not only your disciple but also a man of his word.

291
00:34:56,460 --> 00:35:00,699
Young Master, these are the best medicines in the valley to treat cold toxin.

292
00:35:01,720 --> 00:35:05,399
It's still not enough. Go and get more around the area; the more, the better.

293
00:35:05,399 --> 00:35:10,199
When the time comes, even if I can't cure the cold toxin, it'll be good to buy some time for her.

294
00:35:10,199 --> 00:35:13,900
When Lu Ping undoes his lock, at that time,

295
00:35:13,900 --> 00:35:16,220
how can we not find a way to cure the cold toxin?

296
00:35:16,220 --> 00:35:20,219
Who exactly has the cold toxin? Young Master, what are you talking about?

297
00:35:20,219 --> 00:35:24,799
Why are we talking like this?! No one is here! We—

298
00:35:24,799 --> 00:35:26,511
Just in case.

299
00:35:26,511 --> 00:35:32,051
You can't tell anyone about this, including my father.

300
00:35:32,051 --> 00:35:35,971
If you dare to say a word, I will poison you and make you mute right now.

301
00:35:37,680 --> 00:35:40,971
I will do whatever you ask me to do.

302
00:35:43,040 --> 00:35:47,491
You're good. You're much better than my two brothers.

303
00:35:47,491 --> 00:35:52,771
They are not obedient at all. What would they do without me?

304
00:35:52,771 --> 00:35:54,939
Yes. What would they do?

305
00:35:59,480 --> 00:36:01,319
That Liu Song!

306
00:36:01,320 --> 00:36:05,311
Your Majesty, calm down. They are just using evil means.

307
00:36:05,311 --> 00:36:09,139
Your Majesty has the power of the dragons. There's no need to fear.

308
00:36:10,060 --> 00:36:14,951
When two armies battle on the battlefield, does that depend on the power of the dragons?

309
00:36:15,480 --> 00:36:19,771
It depends on the soldiers and weapons.

310
00:36:20,600 --> 00:36:25,519
Using five Pneumas is the strength of an expert like Yan Qiuci.

311
00:36:25,520 --> 00:36:28,471
If these experts gather to form an army,

312
00:36:28,471 --> 00:36:31,551
ordinary soldiers won't be able to stop them.

313
00:36:33,500 --> 00:36:34,700
Your Majesty,

314
00:36:34,700 --> 00:36:41,219
in my opinion, it's not a bad thing that General Wen has discovered the secret of the Mountain and Sea Gang.

315
00:36:41,219 --> 00:36:44,211
Lu Ping is now under our control.

316
00:36:44,211 --> 00:36:48,531
Why not treat them how we're being treated?

317
00:36:48,531 --> 00:36:51,531
Lu Ping is the Awakener who can use six Pneumas.

318
00:36:51,531 --> 00:36:56,011
With his help, we don't need to fear the Mountain and Sea Gang.

319
00:36:56,011 --> 00:36:59,179
It's an emergency. I hope Your Majesty will make a decision.

320
00:36:59,179 --> 00:37:02,691
Lu Ping must not fall into the hands of others.

321
00:37:02,691 --> 00:37:06,171
Give my orders to Wen Rui and Yan Xifan.

322
00:37:06,860 --> 00:37:10,151
They must bring Lu Ping to me.

323
00:37:11,540 --> 00:37:14,731
Don't let him fall into the hands of the Mountain and Sea Gang.

324
00:37:14,731 --> 00:37:17,371
I will obey your order.

325
00:37:22,040 --> 00:37:27,859
Xifan, I've asked the military physicians to do their best, but the master of the Phoenix Ridge Gang had already stopped breathing.

326
00:37:33,320 --> 00:37:37,079
Xifan, don't be like this. You've done your best.

327
00:37:37,800 --> 00:37:41,839
In order to create Pneuma Soul Eaters, the Mountain and Sea Gang disregards everyone elses lives.

328
00:37:41,839 --> 00:37:45,200
If they succeed, Dan State will take this opportunity to invade the south.

329
00:37:45,200 --> 00:37:48,010
Who knows how many civilians will suffer.

330
00:37:48,011 --> 00:37:51,380
You can't deal with them all by yourself.

331
00:37:51,380 --> 00:37:53,931
You should ask Lu Ping for help.

332
00:37:54,940 --> 00:37:58,959
He has been tormented for so many years. Right now, he can relax at Carefree Valley.

333
00:37:58,959 --> 00:38:02,520
Ziyan, let him live his life in peace.

334
00:38:05,360 --> 00:38:07,971
General Wen, do we need to leave now?

335
00:38:08,640 --> 00:38:11,670
Young Hero Yan, there is an edict from His Majesty,

336
00:38:12,240 --> 00:38:16,851
ordering you to go to Carefree Valley and to bring Lu Ping back with you.

337
00:38:21,680 --> 00:38:23,630
His Majesty wants to deal with the Pneuma Soul Eaters?

338
00:38:23,630 --> 00:38:27,070
He can just get the Agile Dragon Army back to train. What does he want with Lu Ping?

339
00:38:27,079 --> 00:38:31,200
Soldiers only need to listen to orders. They do not need to ask questions.

340
00:38:32,220 --> 00:38:35,739
His Majesty knows that Lu Ping doesn't want to be an official. He usually wouldn't bother him.

341
00:38:36,320 --> 00:38:38,600
Is His Majesty going to follow the Xi Sui of the Mountain and Sea Gang?

342
00:38:38,600 --> 00:38:42,100
His Majesty also said Wuji Manor deceived the emperor.

343
00:38:42,100 --> 00:38:45,899
According to the law, your whole family should have been beheaded, but His Majesty was merciful.

344
00:38:45,899 --> 00:38:50,111
He saw that you were young and talented so he didn't hold your family accountable.

345
00:38:50,111 --> 00:38:54,851
You better not act on impulse and disappoint His Majesty.

346
00:38:54,851 --> 00:38:57,919
Is His Majesty going to use Wuji Manor as a hostage?

347
00:38:57,920 --> 00:39:01,399
Xifan, I beg you.

348
00:39:01,399 --> 00:39:04,960
That day, we all witnessed the power of the master of Phoenix Ridge Gang.

349
00:39:04,960 --> 00:39:09,079
If we don't do something, when the brothers of Agile Dragon Army are in battle one day,

350
00:39:09,079 --> 00:39:12,491
we will only be slaughtered. They are also human.

351
00:39:12,491 --> 00:39:16,659
They are brothers who had accompanied you to the Mountain and Sea Gang to save Lu Ping.

352
00:39:17,320 --> 00:39:20,071
Can you bear watching them die?

353
00:39:28,080 --> 00:39:31,971
I will obey the order.

354
00:39:35,460 --> 00:39:37,251
Miss Ling, please wait.

355
00:39:41,440 --> 00:39:45,240
His Majesty has a second secret edict. It is for you.

356
00:40:00,260 --> 00:40:04,060
Xifan, are you really going to Carefree Valley to bring Lu Ping back?

357
00:40:04,060 --> 00:40:08,599
Mo Lin was afraid we would get separated that day outside of the Mountain and Sea Gang so he gave me a map.

358
00:40:08,599 --> 00:40:12,659
If Liu Song really uses Lu Ping to create the Pneuma Soul Eaters who can use six Pneumas,

359
00:40:12,659 --> 00:40:17,560
the situation will be even more difficult to deal with. I can only bring Lu Ping back to Kaifeng first.

360
00:40:17,560 --> 00:40:19,360
Then try my best to persuade His Majesty.

361
00:40:19,360 --> 00:40:24,351
But Lu Ping has a deep blood feud with His Majesty. What if he won't come back with you?

362
00:40:24,351 --> 00:40:26,460
Will you go against the edict for his sake?

363
00:40:26,460 --> 00:40:29,311
I can only try my best to balance both.

364
00:40:29,311 --> 00:40:31,891
Take a rest. I am going to check on the horses.

365
00:40:45,640 --> 00:40:49,799
Lu Ping must not fall into the hands of the Mountain and Sea Gang. You must bring him back.

366
00:40:49,799 --> 00:40:52,831
If he resists, get rid of him.

367
00:40:52,831 --> 00:40:57,171
If Yan Xifan is soft with Lu Ping, you can help him finish the task.

368
00:40:57,171 --> 00:41:01,011
Otherwise, I won't spare Yan Xifan's life.

369
00:41:01,011 --> 00:41:05,540
Xifan, I definitely won't let you commit the crime of betraying the emperor.

370
00:41:05,540 --> 00:41:08,251
I can only hope this will be resolved smoothly.

371
00:41:16,620 --> 00:41:20,151
Master Mo, why did you bring me here? To enjoy the flowers?

372
00:41:22,120 --> 00:41:24,479
You can recuperate at Carefree Valley,

373
00:41:24,480 --> 00:41:28,039
