377
00:41:49,480 --> 00:41:55,600
Once I undo the Pneuma Confinement, I will go back to my hometown and plant flowers.

378
00:41:56,920 --> 00:42:00,300
I will invite you to go with me then. How about it?

379
00:42:01,520 --> 00:42:04,699
The countryside? What's so good about it?

380
00:42:05,710 --> 00:42:07,110
Never mind then.

381
00:42:15,140 --> 00:42:19,540
Brother, did you think of something?

382
00:42:24,080 --> 00:42:25,380
Open your mouth.

383
00:42:28,480 --> 00:42:31,679
